# NIX DERIVATION
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Manage Nix derivations (.drv files).
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix derivation show nixpkgs#hello: Show the contents of a derivation.

### Essentials
- nix derivation add ... : Create a derivation from a JSON description.

## Tips
- Derivations are the low-level build instructions that Nix uses to create packages.

